# hfydl

**hfydl** is a command-line tool which compiles reddit "next" link chains into epubs.

---

## Installation

```bash
pip install hfydl
```

---

## Usage
```bash
hfydl <start-url> [-o OUTPUT] [-t TITLE] [-a AUTHOR] [-c COVER]
```
